include ../modal/modal

mixin download(data)

	.button.button_circle.download(title=data.title)
		i(class=data.icon)
		//-span.text= data.title
		.download-menu
			ul
				each ent, num in data.links
					li.download-menu__item
						if ent.popup == true
							span(data-remodal-target="modal" + num)= ent.title
							+modal({"id": "modal" + num, "close": true})
								div(style="padding: 15px; width: 400px;")
									p(style="margin: 10px 0;")
										| Are you a user that has not rebooted your mac in a while? Because of an unattended MacOS upgrade that should require a reboot yet does not, the MacOS installer may fail to install properly. Please reboot if you've not done so in a while before launching the installer.

									div(style="text-align: right;")
										button.button.button_style_ghost.button_color_red(data-remodal-action="cancel" class="remodal-cancel") Cancel
										a.button.remodal-confirm(href=ent.href, onclick=ent.action) Got It!
						else
							a(href=ent.href, onclick=ent.action)= ent.title

